<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944950>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. Hipposideros boeadii from Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South-East Sulawesi" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944954>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. Noseleaves of four species of Hipposideros (with hairs omitted). A — H. boeadii (holotype), M28253, Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South-East Sulawesi; B — H. papua, M16951, Biak Island, Papua Province; C — H. galeritus, M28250, Kakenauwe Nature Reserve, Buton Island, South- East Sulawesi; D — H. cervinus, M28249, Lambasango Wildlife Reserve, Buton Island, South- East Sulawesi. Scale = 5 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944958>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. Dorsal (above) and ventral (below) views of the skull and dorsal view of the right half mandible of two species of Hipposideros. A — H. boeadii (holotype), M28253, Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South- East Sulawesi, and B — H. papua, M16951, Biak Island, Papua Province. Scale = 5 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944962>
    dc:description "FIG. 4. Lateral view of the skulls and mandibles of four species of Hipposideros. A — H. boeadii (holo- type), M28253, Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South-East Sulawesi; B — H. papua, M16951, Biak Island, Papua Province; C — H. galeritus, M28250, Kakenauwe Nature Reserve, Buton Island, South-East Sulawesi; D — H. cervinus, M28249, Lambasango Wildlife Reserve, Buton Island, South- East Sulawesi. Scale = 5 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944964>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. Dorsal view of the rostrum of four species of Hipposideros. A — H. boeadii (holotype), M28253, Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South-East Sulawesi; B — H. papua, M16951, Biak Island, Papua Province; C — H. galeritus, M28250, Kakenauwe Nature Reserve, Buton Island, South-East Sulawesi; D —" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3944966>
    dc:description "FIG. 6. Baculum of H. boeadii, M22937, Rawa Aopa Watumohai National Park, South-East Sulawesi. Scale = 1 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3944966/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

